                            <comment id="14147337" author="aw" created="Thu, 25 Sep 2014 04:08:35 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The code looks like this:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;  &lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;/** Shell commands to get users and groups */&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;static&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;final&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;String&lt;/span&gt; LINUX_GET_ALL_USERS_CMD = &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;getent passwd | cut -d: -f1,3&quot;&lt;/span&gt;;
  &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;static&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;final&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;String&lt;/span&gt; LINUX_GET_ALL_GROUPS_CMD = &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;getent group | cut -d: -f1,3&quot;&lt;/span&gt;;
  &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;static&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;final&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;String&lt;/span&gt; MAC_GET_ALL_USERS_CMD = &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;dscl . -list /Users UniqueID&quot;&lt;/span&gt;;
  &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;static&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;final&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;String&lt;/span&gt; MAC_GET_ALL_GROUPS_CMD = &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;dscl . -list /Groups PrimaryGroupID&quot;&lt;/span&gt;;
...
    &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (OS.startsWith(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;Linux&quot;&lt;/span&gt;)) {
      updateMapInternal(uMap, &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;user&quot;&lt;/span&gt;, LINUX_GET_ALL_USERS_CMD, &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;:&quot;&lt;/span&gt;,
          staticMapping.uidMapping);
      updateMapInternal(gMap, &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;group&quot;&lt;/span&gt;, LINUX_GET_ALL_GROUPS_CMD, &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;:&quot;&lt;/span&gt;,
          staticMapping.gidMapping);
    } &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;else&lt;/span&gt; {
      &lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;// Mac
&lt;/span&gt;      updateMapInternal(uMap, &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;user&quot;&lt;/span&gt;, MAC_GET_ALL_USERS_CMD, &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;\\s+&quot;&lt;/span&gt;,
          staticMapping.uidMapping);
      updateMapInternal(gMap, &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;group&quot;&lt;/span&gt;, MAC_GET_ALL_GROUPS_CMD, &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;\\s+&quot;&lt;/span&gt;,
          staticMapping.gidMapping);
    }
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;dscl is &lt;b&gt;only&lt;/b&gt; supported on OS X. getent is supported on Linux, Solaris, FreeBSD, ... Ideally, &apos;LINUX_GET_ALL_USERS_CMD&apos; would get renamed to something less Linux specific, we&apos;d check to see if the OS is Mac, etc. to be much more compatible with other OSes.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
